### Problem to solve

<!--
The banners on the Project overview page are different sizes and the bottom one uses the wrong close ("x") pattern

![Screen_Shot_2021-05-12_at_1.53.05_PM](/uploads/0b998f22c5f76cfa75f1c66a4eb70314/Screen_Shot_2021-05-12_at_1.53.05_PM.png)
-->

The free trail banner does not look correct.

### Proposed solution
We will update the trial banner to use our [banner Vue component](https://gitlab-org.gitlab.io/gitlab-ui/?path=/story/base-banner--default). The changes will look as follow:

![image](/uploads/e6a372846d2732f79d1b47d972832ce1/image.png)


**Note**: The default implementation of the banner might render a huge illustration. In the screenshot above I changed the following: 

```css
/* Default implementation */
.gl-banner-illustration img {
   width: 7.5rem;
}
/*  Scaling down the illustration */
.gl-banner-illustration img {
   width: 2.5rem;
}
```
